lead_paragraph: South African Olympic swimming champion Chad le Clos, who beat Michael Phelps in one of the upsets of the 2012 London Games, announced Monday that both his parents are fighting cancer.

headline.main: Olympic Swimming Champ Le Clos Says Both Parents Have Cancer
